    @InternalUseOnly
@NotExtensible
@ThreadSafety(level=INTERFACE_NOT_THREADSAFE)
public interface ProtocolOp
extends java.io.Serializable
    This interface defines a set of methods that should be implemented by all types of LDAP protocol ops.
